{"type":"answer","id":131771,"parentType":"question","parentId":15593,"uid":27085,"contents":"非常好看，比中共的課本準確很多，而且台灣史也並不片面，超出我的意料。<br>\n想看看中共的歷史地圖嗎？<br>\n=========切割線==========<br>\n<br>\n1.民國<br>\n<br>\n我拍攝的是《簡明中國歷史地圖集》。剛發現居然有這張圖，真的太無恥，把丟失領土的責任全甩鍋。無論從哪個角度，這張圖都是錯誤的。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/cpX5U0c.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cpX5U0c.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/cpX5U0c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n課本上用的這張，雖然有些邊角也不對<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/aexsoyX.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aexsoyX.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/aexsoyX.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n2.秦<br>\n畫秦的時候背面還要加清的疆域，實在不理解這邏輯<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZBvUyNw.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZBvUyNw.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZBvUyNw.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n3.漢<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/bM9128S.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bM9128S.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/bM9128S.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n4.三國，跟你們用的圖差異很大<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NoKYVzm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NoKYVzm.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NoKYVzm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n5.唐 唐疆域變動很大，課本上一般用兩個圖。我看過日本的課本，畫的比第一幅圖還大...<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ylViFu.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ylViFu.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ylViFu.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n第二幅圖<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/hcp8iJx.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hcp8iJx.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/hcp8iJx.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n6.宋<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/nCSHrLf.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nCSHrLf.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nCSHrLf.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n7.元<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZZ85lME.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZZ85lME.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZZ85lME.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n8.明<br>\n明和你們的圖差異也很大<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/R2TCW5m.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/R2TCW5m.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/R2TCW5m.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-18","agreeCount":24,"discussionCount":16}